data.name: lumiaFixerInstructions.Text
data.value:
bricked your lumia? happens to the best of us, lumiafixer is design to help you unbrick it using thor2 (from WDRT)
to get started, make sure you have WDTR (Windows Device Recovery Tool), if not a simple google search should help you get it, you will also need emergency files and the original ffu of your phone
if you have everything ready, click the button below to get started on unbricking your lumia
